trans-unit.source: Represents a collection of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Inline" /> elements.
trans-unit.target: Representa una colección de elementos <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Inline" />.

trans-unit.source: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection" /> defines the allowable child content of the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Paragraph" />, <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Span" />, and <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock" /> elements.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection" /> define el contenido secundario admitido de los elementos <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Paragraph" />, <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Span" /> y <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock" />.

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection> creation is only permitted inside an element that owns an <xref:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection>, such as a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock> or a <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Paragraph>.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection> solo se permite la creación dentro de un elemento al que pertenece un <xref:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection>, como un <xref:System.Windows.Controls.TextBlock> o <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Paragraph>.

trans-unit.source: As such, an <xref:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection> cannot be instantiated directly and has no default or overloaded constructor.
trans-unit.target: Por lo tanto, un <xref:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection> no se pueden crear instancias directamente y no tiene valor predeterminado o sobrecargar el constructor.

trans-unit.source: Adds a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Run" /> element to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Agrega un elemento <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Run" /> a la recolección.

trans-unit.source: Text set as the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Documents.Run.Text" /> property for the implicit <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Run" />.
trans-unit.target: Texto establecido como propiedad <see cref="P:System.Windows.Documents.Run.Text" /> para <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Run" /> implícito.

trans-unit.source: Adds an implicit <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Run" /> element with the given text, supplied as a <see cref="T:System.String" />.
trans-unit.target: Agrega un elemento <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Run" /> implícito con el texto determinado, proporcionado como <see cref="T:System.String" />.

trans-unit.source: <see cref="T:System.Windows.UIElement" /> set as the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer.Child" /> property for the implicit <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer" />.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.UIElement" /> establecido como propiedad <see cref="P:System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer.Child" /> para <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer" /> implícito.

trans-unit.source: Adds an implicit <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer" /> with the supplied <see cref="T:System.Windows.UIElement" /> already in it.
trans-unit.target: Agrega un <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineUIContainer" /> implícito con el <see cref="T:System.Windows.UIElement" /> proporcionado en él.

trans-unit.source: Gets the first <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Inline" /> element within this instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene el primer elemento <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Inline" /> de esta instancia de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The first <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Inline" /> element within this instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Primer elemento <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Inline" /> de esta instancia de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection" />.

trans-unit.target: Obtiene el último elemento <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Inline" /> de esta instancia de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection" />.

trans-unit.source: The last <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Inline" /> element within this instance of <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Último elemento <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.Inline" /> de esta instancia de <see cref="T:System.Windows.Documents.InlineCollection" />.
